    AFL_LLVM_INSTRUMENT=NGRAM-<value> or AFL_LLVM_NGRAM_SIZE=<value>
  - Added llvm_mode context sensitive branch coverage, activated by setting
    AFL_LLVM_INSTRUMENT=CTX or AFL_LLVM_CTX=1
  - llvm_mode InsTrim mode:
